If VAR has a value already, overwrite it. If SAVE-EXCURSION is non-nil, do not
move point to the file-local variables section."
  (modify-file-local-variable var value 'add-or-replace)
  (hack-local-variables)
  (when save-excursion
    (back-button-local 1)))

